-- Playback function
local function playAnimation(loop)
    local startTime = tick()
    local conn
    conn = game:GetService("RunService").Heartbeat:Connect(function()
        local elapsed = tick() - startTime
        if elapsed > keyframes[#keyframes].time then
            if loop then
                startTime = tick()
            else
                conn:Disconnect()
                return
            end
        end
        
        -- Find prev and next keyframe
        local prev, nextKf = keyframes[1], keyframes[1]
        for i = 2, #keyframes do
            if elapsed < keyframes[i].time then
                prev = keyframes[i-1]
                nextKf = keyframes[i]
                break
            end
        end
        
        -- Alpha for lerp
        local duration = nextKf.time - prev.time
        local alpha = (elapsed - prev.time) / duration
        
        -- Apply lerped transforms
        for name, nextCf in pairs(nextKf.poses) do
            local joint = joints[name]
            if joint then
                local prevCf = prev.poses[name]
                joint.Transform = prevCf:Lerp(nextCf, alpha)
            end
        end
    end)
end
